    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Meditation against TN 6\nType: Normal\nQi: 7\n\nStanding you move your arms before your chest and channel a dangerous mixture of phoenix and dragon energy through your meridian points, harnessing them in your center for an explosion of power. Perform this standing meditation as a Move Action. On a Success, for the next 3 rounds, your Melee Attacks deliver normal damage plus 8 Extra Wounds. On a Total Success your melee attacks deliver normal damage plus 15 Extra Wounds and the effect lasts for 4 rounds. On a failure you lose control, attacking the nearest target possible each round until the technique ends, doing normal damage plus 8 Extra wounds. The effect lasts for 5 rounds on a failure.",
